Titulo: Stretching Isn’t Just for Athletes It Boosts Brain Power Too
Resumo: Regular stretching improves blood flow—not just to your muscles, but also to your brain. This increased circulation can enhance mental clarity, focus, and even mood. A few minutes of gentle stretching throughout the day helps break up sedentary time, reduce muscle tension, and refresh your mind, making it a powerful yet simple way to stay sharp and energized.
